      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Angels We Thought We Should Be</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>It's time you count my blessings </l>
          <l>All in one hand </l>
          <l>And burry my watch in the sand </l>
          <l>Rain came and went, </l>
          <l>time wisely spent. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>And while we’re here </l>
          <l>We try to see </l>
          <l>The angels we thought we should be </l>
          <l>Gliding down the slope </l>
          <l>like a cushion full of hope </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>(Now I can see The </l>
          <l>angel I thought I should be </l>
          <l>Am I being him or is it me) </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>The sooner you're waken </l>
          <l>The better you'll be </l>
          <l>I guess you may say that about me </l>
          <l>As I slip into </l>
          <l>rhyme with a mild trace of lime </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>(Now I should be </l>
          <l>The angel I thought I could see </l>
          <l>Am I being him or is it me)</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
